{"tid":2256480,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得納粹殺人, 同黑警果種香港市民係曱甴既慨念好相似?","createTime":"2020-10-24T11:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T18:44:31.000Z","uid":81236,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"adcc714fc22ddfd33928321bbdd5d06420130647","tid":2256480,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:33:18.000Z","msg":"係第二次世界大戰, 佢地視希特拉為英雄, <br />\n佢地覺得猶太入侵佢地國家, 直接清洗佢地種族,仲會搶佢地資源, <br />\n但美國太強, 所以佢地種下的罪孽,過兩年就受返<br />\n而猶太種族清洗就係一種踏浪的慨念,<br />\n對納粹黎講, 猶太人無一個係無辜, <br />\n對敵人同情, 係左膠行為,<br />\n所以種族清洗可視為踏浪行動<br />\n<br />\n將警犬果代慨念,完全Key到納粹殺人, <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上係正常人既理解, 黑警角度未必係岩, 唔好信以為真, 無意去誤導大家<br />\n純粹想同大家討論一下"},{"pid":"cb1e8798e44c66817029daa8e6d30196df6dc705","tid":2256480,"uid":81236,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:33:49.000Z","msg":"其實我都說服左呢個POST 唔少藍絲,<br />\n但太多人回POST, 覆唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb0583dc197f6d8c8cd90ce59b25a771c0e584e","tid":2256480,"uid":372131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"613ef9b66c1a2f50473d822090306cd808545db0","tid":2256480,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bb0583dc197f6d8c8cd90ce59b25a771c0e584e","tid":2256480,"uid":372131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:36:56.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb59d9a0965b38af1b95ef18b7339eed6079fed","tid":2256480,"uid":372131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"613ef9b66c1a2f50473d822090306cd808545db0","tid":2256480,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bb0583dc197f6d8c8cd90ce59b25a771c0e584e","tid":2256480,"uid":372131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:36:56.000Z","ms